entry.title: dhsu/euler-scala
entry.summary:
Learning scala through project euler

euler-scala

Learning scala through project euler (http://projecteuler.net).

With the exception of extending trait, Problem, each problem implementation is self-contained. This is intentional because it forced the reimplementation of common mathematical functions such as isPrime and isPandigital.
